a.n: The stepmother 7: Ash Hollywood & Seth Gamble

p.k: Lynn has it all, a caring successful husband in a sumptuous Hollywood mansion, but something is missing. When her husband's daughter comes to visit with her new boyfriend, Chuck, Veronica's passion for acting is re-awakened by the young movie star. The Stepmother Vol. 07 is a thoughtful look at forgotten passions and submerged desires.
